# HACCP-Online — Cursor Rules

## Project
SaaS for HACCP/SanPiN electronic journals at food production facilities (CIS market).
Private repo: https://github.com/djdes/HACCP-Online

## Stack
- Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript, React 19
- Prisma 7 with @prisma/adapter-pg (PostgreSQL)
- NextAuth.js 4 (JWT + Credentials)
- shadcn/ui (new-york style) + TailwindCSS 4
- Zod v4, Lucide icons, Sonner toasts

## Setup
```bash
cp .env.shared .env && npm install && npx prisma generate && npx prisma db push && npx tsx prisma/seed.ts && npm run dev
```

## Key Rules
- UI text in Russian. Code/comments in English.
- Page params are Promises in Next.js 16: always `const { code } = await params`
- Use `sonner` for toasts, never shadcn `toast` (deprecated)
- Path alias: `@/*` → `./src/*`
- Prisma 7 requires `@prisma/adapter-pg` pool — see `src/lib/db.ts`
- Zod v4 (not v3)
- All data multi-tenant: scope queries by `session.user.organizationId`
- Three roles: owner > technologist > operator
- API routes: `getServerSession(authOptions)` → role check → Zod validate → Prisma → NextResponse.json()
- Notifications (email/Telegram) are fire-and-forget: catch errors, don't fail main operation

## Architecture
- `(auth)/` — login, register (public)
- `(dashboard)/` — sidebar layout, protected by `requireAuth()`
- `src/lib/` — auth.ts, db.ts, validators.ts, email.ts, telegram.ts, tuya.ts, pdf.ts
- `prisma/schema.prisma` — 6 models: Organization, User, Area, Equipment, JournalTemplate, JournalEntry

## Git Workflow
Never push to master directly. Use feature branches + PR:
```bash
git checkout -b feature/name
# code...
git push -u origin feature/name
gh pr create
```

## Deployment
See CLAUDE.md for full deploy script. Server: 192.168.33.3, PM2 on port 3001.
Secrets in `.env.shared`. Deploy helpers (`_deploy.py`, `_run.py`) are in .gitignore.
